Then both handlers become thin wrappers calling `validateAndRespond`.

## 3. Extract shared template card builder

In `src/fragments/setup.ts`, `templateSelectionFragment` and in `src/fragments/program.ts`, `importTemplateSelectionFragment` share the same sort + map + card HTML logic. Extract a shared function. The only difference is the `data-on:click` attribute per card.

